Description: DNS static entry management for MikroTik routers
 Mikro DNS provides comprehensive DNS management for MikroTik routers
 via the RouterOS API. Features include:
  * List, add, update, delete DNS entries
  * Support for all record types (A, AAAA, CNAME, MX, TXT, NS, SRV, etc.)
  * Search with wildcards
  * Enable/disable entries
  * Validate for conflicts
  * Import/export (JSON/CSV)
  * Auto-register servers
